And here, I'll
refer you to a book

00:54:23.656 --> 00:54:28.690
by Jill Bolte called
"My Stroke of Insight."

00:54:28.690 --> 00:54:29.670
She was a--

00:54:29.670 --> 00:54:31.630
I think she was a
doctor or a pathologist

00:54:31.630 --> 00:54:33.340
or something of that kind.

00:54:33.340 --> 00:54:34.920
And she had a stroke.

00:54:34.920 --> 00:54:36.550
And with the stroke,
what happened

00:54:36.550 --> 00:54:39.520
was the left side of her
brain was totally paralyzed,

00:54:39.520 --> 00:54:41.432
and only the right
side was working.

00:54:41.432 --> 00:54:43.390
You know, we have a left
brain and right brain.

00:54:46.100 --> 00:54:49.960
See the left brain is the
one that calculates and says,

00:54:49.960 --> 00:54:53.770
oh, when you say you are
[? m, ?] your consciousness

00:54:53.770 --> 00:54:58.530
is confined to this
limit only, not here.

00:54:58.530 --> 00:55:03.700
It'd be mad if I said,
this is [? m, ?] normally.

00:55:03.700 --> 00:55:06.835
In this lady's case,
the calculating brain,

00:55:06.835 --> 00:55:08.770
which decides your
space and time

00:55:08.770 --> 00:55:13.630
dimensions, which is the
left, was kind of completely

00:55:13.630 --> 00:55:14.340
paralyzed.

00:55:14.340 --> 00:55:17.920
She recovered enough to write
about it, of course, later.

00:55:17.920 --> 00:55:22.510
And her right brain was
fully awake, still working.

00:55:22.510 --> 00:55:26.440
That's when, according
to her, she figured out

00:55:26.440 --> 00:55:30.100
that when she was in the room
and there were these birds

00:55:30.100 --> 00:55:35.300
outside and the breeze blowing
and the leaves shaking,

00:55:35.300 --> 00:55:39.670
it was not as if the leaves
were moving, she was moving.

00:55:39.670 --> 00:55:43.240
It was not as if the birds
were singing, she was singing.

00:55:43.240 --> 00:55:47.100
She was not singing,
but she was singing!

00:55:47.100 --> 00:55:49.430
You get what I'm trying to say?

00:55:49.430 --> 00:55:53.260
So I'm not saying we
should all have a brain

00:55:53.260 --> 00:55:55.630
hemorrhage to experience this.

00:55:55.630 --> 00:55:59.080
I'm saying that there are ways
and means in yoga by which this

00:55:59.080 --> 00:56:03.160
can be brought about
without a hemorrhage.

00:56:03.160 --> 00:56:05.940
So after that,
once you feel that,

00:56:05.940 --> 00:56:07.810
then you cannot be the same.

00:56:07.810 --> 00:56:09.940
Your life changes.

00:56:09.940 --> 00:56:12.390
You can't be the same.

00:56:12.390 --> 00:56:13.940
I think that's self-evident.

00:56:19.660 --> 00:56:21.243
PRASAD SETTY: Maybe
one more question.

00:56:21.243 --> 00:56:22.209
Yes?

00:56:22.209 --> 00:56:23.658
SRI M: Ah, only one.

