AUDIENCE: My name is Vic--

00:56:28.590 --> 00:56:29.430
Vivek.

00:56:29.430 --> 00:56:30.790
Thank you for coming.

00:56:30.790 --> 00:56:31.794
SRI M: What's your name?

00:56:31.794 --> 00:56:32.460
AUDIENCE: Vivek.

00:56:32.460 --> 00:56:33.450
Vivek Rao.

00:56:33.450 --> 00:56:34.680
SRI M: Vivek.

