AUDIENCE: My sister was
on the walk with you.

00:56:36.600 --> 00:56:37.562
Her name is Sunita.

00:56:37.562 --> 00:56:39.250
SRI M: Oh, Sunita!

00:56:39.250 --> 00:56:41.430
We have a big joke, you know.

00:56:41.430 --> 00:56:45.270
That when we entered Nashik,
from somewhere a monkey

00:56:45.270 --> 00:56:47.352
came down, and bit her.

00:56:47.352 --> 00:56:48.060
PRASAD SETTY: Oh.

00:56:48.060 --> 00:56:49.844
SRI M: Yeah, so
nothing happened.

00:56:49.844 --> 00:56:51.010
We gave her some injections.

00:56:51.010 --> 00:56:52.315
She was fine.

00:56:52.315 --> 00:56:53.190
But I have this joke.

00:56:53.190 --> 00:56:54.910
Every time I see her,
